Author: q66 <q66@chimera-linux.org>
Date:   Thu May 7 11:42:06 2026 +0200

    revert broken jacobiSvd invocations
    
    Stuff like X.jacobiSvd(arg)... was converted to a template
    invocation as a part of removal of ceres/eigen from core in
    https://github.com/blender/blender/commit/18a01ebc6b0dda3fb0372757765391990de45fdb
    for seemingly no good reason. This now breaks with system
    versions of the libs.

diff --git a/intern/dualcon/intern/octree.cpp b/intern/dualcon/intern/octree.cpp
